gue","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/jose-mourinho-co-nguy-co-bi-sa-thai-cao-nhat-tai-premier-league.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c h\u00e3ng c\u00e1 c\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i Anh \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean Jose Mourinho l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi cao h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai sau nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Man Utd trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Daily Mail \u0111\u01b0a tin, c\u00e1c h\u00e3ng c\u00e1 c\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i Anh \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0a ra t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 Jose Mourinho b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i cao nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng sau Mourinho l\u00e0 Claude Puel (Leicester), Javi Gracia (Watford) v\u00e0 Rafa Benitez (Newcastle).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/mourinho-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1edf d\u0129 Mourinho n\u1eb1m \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u trong nh\u00f3m nh\u1eefng hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0 do th\u00e0nh t\u00edch k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a Man Utd trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018. Tr\u1ea3i qua 4 tr\u1eadn, Man Utd ch\u01b0a th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o sau 90 ph\u00fat (3 h\u00f2a, 1 thua).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Man Utd c\u0169ng \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Nemanja Matic, Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Ander Herrera. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1edf hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1edfi k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o t\u1ea1i ICC 2018<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn thua Liverpool v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-4 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu ICC 2018, HLV Jose Mourinho g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \"kh\u00f4ng mua v\u00e9 xem c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ebf n\u00e0y\". Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, h\u01a1n 100.000 c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho Man Utd v\u00e0 Liverpool.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i c\u1ee7a Mourinho, Charlie Stillitano - ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh ICC c\u1ee7a Relevent Sports chia s\u1ebb: \"T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. Mourinho mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean, cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 cho \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. Mourinho mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c trong m\u1ed9t n\u0103m World Cup di\u1ec5n ra\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi g\u1eb7p Real Madrid, Jose Mourinho s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Nemanja Matic, Marcos Rojo, Antonio Valencia v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng Paul Pogba, Romelu Lukaku, Marouane Fellaini, Phil Jones, Ashley Young, Jesse Lingard v\u00e0 Marcus Rashford \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 sau World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anthony Martial kh\u00f4ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i sau khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Ph\u00e1p ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 ra \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a con th\u1ee9 hai.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho h\u00e8 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-307-jose-mourinho-cau-cuu-nhom-tru-cot-man-utd-184-192346.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 30/7: Jose Mourinho c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u nh\u00f3m tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-dieu-mourinho-can-lam-de-cuu-van-tour-du-dau-tham-hoa-cua-mu-172-192341.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u Mourinho c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 MU kh\u00f4ng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-khung-hoang-tien-mua-giai-khi-van-de-khong-chi-la-luc-luong-172-192337.html\">M.U kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i: Khi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-to-x/goc-nhin-dau-co-gi-la-khi-mourinho-yeu-harry-maguire-393-192312.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: \u0110\u00e2u c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u1ea1 khi Mourinho y\u00eau Harry Maguire?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuu-sao-mu-noi-do-cho-hai-cai-ten-trong-danh-sach-den-cua-mourinho-172-192306.html\">C\u1ef1u sao MU n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong \u201cdanh s\u00e1ch \u0111en\u201d c\u1ee7a Mourinho</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-don-sieu-bao-chan-thuong-truoc-them-dai-chien-real-172-192304.html\">MU d\u00ednh si\u00eau b\u00e3o ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Real</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4844","checkdouble":"192349"},{"date":"21:56 30/07","title":"Nh\u1edd Joe Gomez, Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng \"ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t\" \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/nho-joe-gomez-jurgen-klopp-khong-mua-them-hau-ve.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Joe Gomez, HLV Jurgen Klopp t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0o cho Liverpool trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp tin v\u00e0o Joe Gomez<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi ra h\u01a1n 174 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed1n c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u1ed3m Alisson Becker, Naby Keita, Fabinho v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ai thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 l\u00e0m n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u suy \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1eb1ng Liverpool s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1edd Joe Gomez, Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1edd Joe Gomez, Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/nho-joe-gomez-jurgen-klopp-khong-mua-them-hau-ve.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nh\u1edd Joe Gomez, Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool t\u1eebng chi ra 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung trung v\u1ec7 Virgil Van Dijk h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a The Kop c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn, ngo\u00e0i Van Dijk c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Ragnar Klavan, Dejan Lovren, Joel Matip v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Joe Gomez.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Joe Gomez: \"C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Joe Gomez m\u00e0 HLV Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 cho Liverpool h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh nh\u01b0 Fabinho hay James Milner c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Klopp t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 The Kop.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp chia s\u1ebb: \"C\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y ch\u01b0a c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f2n 12 ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa trong th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. N\u00ean gi\u1edd t\u00f4i n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ebfn mai khi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecfi, c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00e1c\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool \u0111ang kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t khi th\u1eafng Man City v\u00e0 Man Utd trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Liverpool h\u00e8 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/van-dijk-liverpool-da-san-sang-lam-nhung-dieu-dac-biet-172-192321.html\">Van Dijk: Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/aston-villa-hoi-muon-ben-woodburn-172-192317.html\">Aston Villa h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n sao tr\u1ebb s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huy-diet-mu-klopp-danh-loi-ca-ngoi-cho-1-cai-ten-172-192240.html\">H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t M.U, Klopp d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i cho 1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-14-liverpool-icc-2018-326-192224.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 1-4 Liverpool (ICC 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-dat-nhat-the-gioi-klopp-van-khen-re-172-192219.html\">Alisson \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Klopp v\u1eabn khen... r\u1ebb</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-xet-liverpool-tiet-lo-dang-yeu-lai-tu-dau-voi-klopp-172-192212.html\">Sao x\u1eb9t Liverpool ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111ang \u201cy\u00eau l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u\u201d v\u1edbi Klopp</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4843","checkdouble":"192350"},{"date":"00:32 31/07","title":"Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp: Ai chi ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/jose-mourinho-va-jurgen-klopp-ai-chi-tien-chuyen-nhuong-nhieu-hon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea1o chi tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1eefa Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp, nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng hai chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ch\u00edn, m\u1ed9t m\u01b0\u1eddi.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ai chi nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu x\u00e9t t\u1eeb c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c th\u00e1ng 5/2016 khi Jose Mourinho b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Man Utd, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n hai chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia \u0111\u1ed5 v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch nhau l\u00e0 bao. Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 411.55* tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn trong n\u0103m d\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ecbch 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho va Jurgen Klopp deu chi rat nhieu tien tren thi truong chuyen nhuong.\" title=\"Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u1ec1u chi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/jose-mourinho-va-jurgen-klopp-ai-chi-tien-chuyen-nhuong-nhieu-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u1ec1u chi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, Klopp th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y Liverpool chi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Virgil Van Dijk. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, The Klopp b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam b\u1ed1n g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t g\u1ed3m Alisson Becker (67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), Naby Keita (53.75), Fabinho (43) v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri (13.5).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Jose Mourinho trong hai n\u0103m qua c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ti\u00eau t\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Man Utd s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 392.55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n Man Utd chi ra tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda Liverpool v\u1edbi ba b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Fred (53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), Diogo Dalot (19) v\u00e0 Lee Grant (1.5).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ai hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t danh hi\u1ec7u, Jose Mourinho \u0111ang nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n khi \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 3 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch cho Man Utd. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Carabao Cup 2016-17, Europa League 2016-17 v\u00e0 FA Community Shield 2016. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Jurgen Klopp ba l\u1ea7n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec, ch\u01b0a gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 l\u00e3i tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Jurgen Klopp l\u1ea1i nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n. Liverpool thu v\u1ec1 289.65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong hai n\u0103m qua, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 The Kop ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 chi ra 121.9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Mourinho ch\u1ec9 thu v\u1ec1 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 85.3 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf Man Utd ph\u1ea3i b\u00f9 th\u00eam ra l\u1edbn g\u1ea5p r\u01b0\u1ee1i Liverpool v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 307.25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>* S\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u t\u1eeb Sky Sports.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Mourinho v\u00e0 Klopp:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-co-nguy-co-bi-sa-thai-cao-nhat-tai-premier-league-172-192349.html\">Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-307-jose-mourinho-cau-cuu-nhom-tru-cot-man-utd-184-192346.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 30/7: Jose Mourinho c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u nh\u00f3m tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-dieu-mourinho-can-lam-de-cuu-van-tour-du-dau-tham-hoa-cua-mu-172-192341.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u Mourinho c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 MU kh\u00f4ng r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 2018/19</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nho-joe-gomez-jurgen-klopp-khong-mua-them-hau-ve-172-192350.html\">Nh\u1edd Joe Gomez, Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huy-diet-mu-klopp-danh-loi-ca-ngoi-cho-1-cai-ten-172-192240.html\">H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t M.U, Klopp d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i cho 1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alisson-dat-nhat-the-gioi-klopp-van-khen-re-172-192219.html\">Alisson \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Klopp v\u1eabn khen... r\u1ebb</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4842","checkdouble":"192353"},{"date":"06:17 31/07","title":"Cesar Azpilicueta n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 HLV Sarri?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/cesar-azpilicueta-noi-gi-ve-hlv-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cesar Azpilicueta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Maurizio Sarri, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Azpilicueta \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao HLV Sarri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-chelsea-sa-thai-hlv-antonio-conte-465-191114.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i HLV Conte</span> v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Maurizio Sarri. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cesar Azpilicueta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Maurizio Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cesar Azpilicueta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Maurizio Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/cesar-azpilicueta-noi-gi-ve-hlv-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Azpilicueta \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao HLV Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCesar Azpilicueta ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 HLV Maurizio Sarri, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t l\u00ean\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cChelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. Nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u00edch nghi t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0o Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Chelsea s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Man City, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Azpilicueta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Sarri th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 khi c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0y \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Azpilicueta noi ve tran dau Barca vs Chelsea\" title=\"Azpilicueta n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/16/Azpilicueta-phat-bieu-ve-tinh-canh-bi-dat-cua-Chelsea-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Azpilicueta s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Cesar Azpilicueta th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 trong h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Conte, m\u00f9a t\u1edbi r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o th\u00ec anh c\u0169ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o mi\u1ec5n l\u00e0 HLV c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4841","checkdouble":"192354"},{"date":"06:34 31/07","title":"BTC ICC t\u1ecf ra th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Mourinho v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/30/btc-icc-to-ra-thong-cam-voi-mourinho-ve-luc-luong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu ICC Charlie Stillitano \u2013 HLV Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 d\u00f9 M.U tr\u1ea3i qua v\u00f4 v\u00e0n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1eeb giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Liverpool h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1, trong \u0111\u00f3 Mourinho th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 r\u1eb1ng, l\u00fac n\u00e0y M.U kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, khi h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c nhau.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed3ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf ICC &ndash; \u00f4ng Charlie Stillitano cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. Jose Mourinho mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 cam k\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf tour du \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1n gi\u00e1, ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i (ICC), v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u1ea3 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u00f4ng \u1ea5y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eed th\u00e1ch trong m\u1ed9t n\u0103m World Cup, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u00f2n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n v\u00ec Premier League di\u1ec5n ra s\u1edbm. \u0110\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn d\u00e0nh cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, Mourinho \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 n\u00f3i l\u00ean quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 b\u1edfi BTC gi\u1ea3i ICC\" title=\"Jose Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1ecb nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t gh\u1ebf cao nh\u1ea5t.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/diem-tin-toi-307-jose-mourinho-cau-cuu-nhom-tru-cot-man-utd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 b\u1edfi BTC gi\u1ea3i ICC</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o n\u0103m t\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ee9, nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao n\u0103m sau kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i World Cup n\u00ean m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd vui m\u1eebng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2019, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec nh\u01b0 n\u0103m nay.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u00f3 l\u1ebd, t\u00f4i l\u00e0 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a CLB h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Mourinho, d\u00f9 l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Mourinho. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh (Liverpool), trong m\u1ed9t SV\u0110 c\u00f3 100 ngh\u00ecn C\u0110V. Mourinho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a gi\u1ea3i ICC l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y, m\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c HLV tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t vui l\u00f2ng khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng&rdquo; &ndash; Charlie Stillitano k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u ICC, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u00f4ng c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a BL\u0110 tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-va-jurgen-klopp-ai-chi-tien-chuyen-nhuong-nhieu-hon-172-192353.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/jose-mourinho-va-jurgen-klopp-ai-chi-tien-chuyen-nhuong-nhieu-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-va-jurgen-klopp-ai-chi-tien-chuyen-nhuong-nhieu-hon-172-192353.html\">Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp: Ai chi ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n?</span><br>\r\nKhi so s\u00e1nh v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea1o chi tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1eefa Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 Jurgen Klopp, nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng hai chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ch\u00edn, m\u1ed9t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-khung-hoang-tien-mua-giai-khi-van-de-khong-chi-la-luc-luong-172-192337.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/mu-khung-hoang-tien-mua-giai-khi-van-de-khong-chi-la-luc-luong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-khung-hoang-tien-mua-giai-khi-van-de-khong-chi-la-luc-luong-172-192337.html\">M.U kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i: Khi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\n4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, 0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng (t\u00ednh trong 90 ph\u00fat) &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ch\u00ednh Mourinho khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1eb7p kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4840","checkdouble":"192359"},{"date":"15:47 30/07","title":"V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Messi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/vo-chong-messi-lien-tuc-gap-nguoi-noi-tieng-trong-ky-nghi-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt VIP ch\u1ecdn Ibiza \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u00e1t, g\u1eb7p si\u00eau sao Argentina v\u00e0 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh chung.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf qu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea3o Turks v\u00e0 Caicos \u1edf v\u00f9ng Carib\u00ea, Messi v\u00e0 Antonella Roccuzzo \u0111ang \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf Ibiza v\u1edbi ba \u0111\u1ee9a con t\u1ea1i Ibiza, T\u00e2y Ban Nha. C\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 \u0111ang tranh th\u1ee7 x\u1ea3 h\u01a1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Messi t\u1eadp trung tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng Barca, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Messi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Messi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/cc-3730-1532830771.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Messi v\u00e0 v\u1ee3 ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u00f9ng ca s\u0129 Gloria Estefan (th\u1ee9 hai t\u1eeb ph\u1ea3i sang). \u1ea2nh: NN.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh tr\u00ean du thuy\u1ec1n ra kh\u01a1i t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng n\u01b0\u1edbc bi\u1ec3n xanh, v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Messi c\u0169ng th\u1ec9nh tho\u1ea3ng l\u00ean b\u1edd, \u0111i th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c b\u1eefa t\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea3o. Ch\u1ed7 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng sang tr\u1ecdng \"Lio\" l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u1ee7a hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Messi v\u00e0 Antonella Roccuzzo g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng si\u00eau sao Argentina m\u1edbi ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh chung c\u00f9ng tay v\u1ee3t Nadal. Ng\u00e0y 27/7, c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u1ed9i ng\u1ed9 ca s\u0129 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 g\u1ed1c Cuba Gloria Estefan. Trong su\u1ed1t chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Ibiza, gia \u0111\u00ecnh Messi c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \"c\u1eb7p k\u00e8\" c\u00f9ng nh\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n Fabregas. L\u00fd do l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea v\u00e0 v\u1ee3 m\u1edbi c\u01b0\u1edbi Daniella Semaan t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ti\u1ec7c sau \u0111\u00e1m c\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n Sant Miquel tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u00eam ti\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Ibiza, Messi v\u00e0 Antonella Roccuzzo c\u0169ng t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t danh th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0 Chelsea - l\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi c\u1ee7a v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Fabregas.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1eafp t\u1edbi, DJ Sebastian Gamboa t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c show di\u1ec5n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea3o T\u00e2y Ban Nha, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n thu h\u00fat nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng. Messi v\u00e0 v\u1ee3 r\u1ea5t m\u00ea nh\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a ngh\u1ec7 s\u0129 qu\u00ea \u1edf \u0111\u1ea3o Ibiza n\u00e0y, \"ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u00fa v\u1ecb\".</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4839","checkdouble":"192329"},{"date":"15:51 30/07","title":"\u0110\u01b0a c\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 sang M\u1ef9, Rooney v\u1eabn c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 \u1edf Anh","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/dua-ca-nha-sang-my-rooney-van-cai-tao-biet-thu-o-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o DC United quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng, b\u1ed5 sung ti\u1ec7n \u00edch cho n\u01a1i \u1edf t\u1ea1i x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf v\u00f9ng Chesire, Anh c\u1ee7a Rooney v\u00e0 Coleen \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p. Theo \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m m\u1edbi, nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00eam. Trong \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1eadp trung l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng camera gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t kh\u1ee7ng ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n cao.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u01b0a gia \u0111\u00ecnh sang M\u1ef9, nh\u00e0 Rooney \u1edf Anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u01b0a gia \u0111\u00ecnh sang M\u1ef9, nh\u00e0 Rooney \u1edf Anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/cc-7752-1532829340.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 t\u1ea1i Anh c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 Rooney \u0111ang n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p. \u1ea2nh: TS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fd do l\u00e0 Rooney - Coleen mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c v\u1edbi n\u1ea1n tr\u1ed9m c\u1eafp m\u00e0 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng l\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n. N\u0103m 2016, khi Coleen c\u00f9ng l\u0169 tr\u1ebb t\u1edbi s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng xem m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Rooney, \"nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng m\u1eddi\" \u0111\u1ed9t nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 v\u00e0 l\u1ea5y \u0111i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1eadt gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb. V\u1ee5 \u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1ee7 \u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m thu\u00ea c\u0169 trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f3 t\u00ean Robert McNamara. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecb k\u1ebft \u00e1n hai n\u0103m 8 th\u00e1ng t\u00f9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb tr\u1ed9m h\u1ecfi th\u0103m bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 c\u00e0ng t\u0103ng cao khi Rooney \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ee3 con t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 sinh s\u1ed1ng khi anh t\u1edbi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o DC United m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, gia \u0111\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1985 d\u00e0nh kho\u1ea3ng n\u1eeda th\u1eddi gian trong n\u0103m \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 \u1edf x\u1ee9 s\u1edf c\u1edd hoa v\u00e0 6 th\u00e1ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i v\u1edbi garage 6 xe, ph\u00f2ng chi\u1ebfu phim mini, b\u1ec3 b\u01a1i, s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 hai h\u1ed3 c\u00e2u \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 Rooney - Coleen \u0111ang \u1edf M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ca gia dinh song o ca Anh va My thoi gian toi. Anh: NS.\" title=\"C\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh s\u1ed1ng \u1edf c\u1ea3 Anh v\u00e0 M\u1ef9 th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. \u1ea2nh: NS.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/cc2-8050-1532829488.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh s\u1ed1ng \u1edf c\u1ea3 Anh v\u00e0 M\u1ef9 th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. \u1ea2nh: NS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4838","checkdouble":"192330"}]}